  🧠 **Fixed.** The race condition is resolved:
     
     - **Root[0m[2m cause**: The `if self.stock >= amount` check and `self.stock -= amount` decrement were separated by an `await asyncio.sleep(0[0m[2m.1)`. This allowed concurrent coroutines to all pass the check before any had decremented — classic time[0m[2m-of-check to time-of-use (TOCTOU) race.
     
     - **Fix**: Added `asyncio.Lock` to make the entire check[0m[2m-and-decrement atomic. Only one coroutine can hold the lock at a time, ensuring no overselling.
     
     - **Result**: [0m[2m3 purchases succeeded (9 items), 2 were correctly rejected, final stock is[0m[2m **1** (never negative).[0m[2m
